{"tid":1588594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我可以預言9.29日唔會太多人","createTime":"2019-09-23T01:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T07:13:02.000Z","uid":113373,"like":32,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8447f2b6b3a30f2b76b8ddb14d1809bd34889834","tid":1588594,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:38:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原因係赤納粹chinazi太離地<br />\n唔係個個香港人都咁有歷史觀，知道咩係納粹<br />\n而納粹又同中國甚至港府有咩關係<br />\n<br />\n如果真係想號召到最多人出嚟，就必須加入更加多貼地嘅主題，貼地嘅口號，包括反極權 反獨裁 捍衛自由 徹查警暴 話我美好香港 等等<br />\n<br />\n唔係個個 都可以將港共政策政治層面問題升級到國家，國際層面</span></strong>"},{"pid":"27d6b283063d7638fbb78a4ecca3a0cd40cdc8a1","tid":1588594,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"e63a361298ee013e490048225583923dd5798cd2","tid":1588594,"uid":113373,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:42:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同埋派傳單文宣等等嘅工作要加密進行， 唔好淨係靠連儂牆，呢個係被動嘅做法<br />\n<br />\n我哋係要主動解釋同同佢哋講，我哋做緊乜，點解要咁做</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">運動同社區一定要有連結，即所謂政治入屋<br />\n<br />\n當運動開始離地，越嚟越多人唔明白手足做緊乜，雖然唔會變為反感，但一定會冷淡落嚟，唔會咁有心去參與</span>"},{"pid":"239e840b854d8832aa11cf75b13ac3a26712433c","tid":1588594,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:42:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9e0c08771b4b21de21fc95daf584fce57243af2","tid":1588594,"uid":113373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:43:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>要connect 最多香港唔同階層嘅人<br />\n<br />\n同時，要開始返大量派文宣，傳單嘅工作</strong></span>"},{"pid":"e66b858d7dabee24b2371551cad848480e159deb","tid":1588594,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:43:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f71ef421e6faea9d9c14ff9e2af7dc3f5b40b7d","tid":1588594,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:43:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62af1798747701d84de830b989497399a3a37112","tid":1588594,"uid":159216,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:44:34.000Z","msg":"其實依家個個星期出黎 真係咁多人關心當日個主題咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a43ff2151bc6481bb5bffc15fba0dab7bab3f56","tid":1588594,"uid":113373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:45:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UcdMshU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUcdMshU.jpg&h=94a444a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WAu9wf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WAu9wf.jpg&h=c4e34f62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gWTpdXW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgWTpdXW.jpg&h=476d2e23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pTmm0CW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpTmm0CW.jpg&h=8b50ab86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CRwaTXX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCRwaTXX.jpg&h=3f8ee864&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33f49b0b5f301a532da1a1e9fb13f85146160b2e","tid":1588594,"uid":90100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:45:35.000Z","msg":"文宣開始"},{"pid":"5370d4ffa5d9e87c2fd113b7d88cc46aed8307ab","tid":1588594,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/an